# Emergency Centre can run without environment variables in the browser-only baseline.
# The optional local API server supports:
#
# EC_API_PORT=8787
# EC_API_ORIGIN=http://localhost:8787
# EC_PROVIDER_USER_AGENT=Emergency Centre/1.0 (+https://github.com/Ninezel/emergency-centre)
#
# `EC_API_PORT` controls the Node API server port.
# `EC_API_ORIGIN` lets the Vite client proxy target a different API origin in development.
# `EC_PROVIDER_USER_AGENT` lets self-hosters set a clearer upstream user agent for official provider requests.
